10. Visualize the 'Category' column from the Shipmode column dataset standpoints.

In[]:
# Create a FacetGrid
cat_hist = sns.FacetGrid(df, col='ship_mode')
cat_hist.map(plt.hist, 'category')

# Get titles from each subplot and modify them
for ax in cat_hist.axes.flat:
    title = ax.get_title()
    modified_title = title.split('=')[-1].strip()
    ax.set_title(modified_title)

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()

# Calculate and plot the SMA line
sales_by_year_month['sma'] = sales_by_year_month['sales'].rolling(window=3).mean()
sns.lineplot(data=sales_by_year_month, x='mon_year', y='sma', color='red', ax=axs, label='SMA (3-Month)')

# Set the figure title
fig.suptitle('Total sales values by year and month', fontsize=16, y=1.05, fontweight='bold')

fig.tight_layout()
plt.show()

END
